## Goal

The focus of this guide is to show you how to setup an IDE to build and run UE4. 

## Objectives

After working through this tutorial, you'll know the following:

* How to configure your IDE to build UE4 in debug and release mode.
* How to configure your IDE to run UE4 in debug and release mode.
* How to build UE4 from your IDE.
* How to run UE4 from your IDE.
* How to create and configure a new Blueprint project from your IDE.
* How to create and configure a new CPP project from your IDE.

